# Place your advertisement videos in this folder

# Naming convention: ad1.mp4, ad2.mp4, ad3.mp4, etc.
# Videos will play in sequential order and loop continuously
# Supported formats: MP4 (recommended), WebM, MOV

# Example structure:
# ad1.mp4 - Promotes new services
# ad2.mp4 - Shows facility tour
# ad3.mp4 - Highlights staff testimonials

# See README.md for detailed instructions
